	\item Relative deviation in peak wall pressure (target: <10\%);
	\item Comparison of total energy dissipation ratio $\eta$ between experimental and numerical results.
\end{itemize}

Although the experimental work is not yet completed, this framework provides a reproducible plan for validation once data become available. It ensures consistency between the numerical and physical models and allows the model’s predictive capability to be rigorously assessed.

